    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Nos <persName ref="#people/167">Landulfus</persName> divina ordinante
                        providentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <name ref="Maio">Maioni</name> fideli nostri, concedimus et confirmamus
                        vobis <name ref="Garofalus">Garofali</name> et <name ref="Mirus"
                            >Miroli</name> et <name ref="Marcanolus">Marcanoli</name> et <name
                            ref="Sichenolfus">Sichenolfi</name> fratris famuli nostri filii <name
                            ref="Piniolus">Pinioli</name>
                        <rs
                            key="#Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >terris exfundatis</rs> et quantas de ipsa <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Residential #Palatium">domnicalia</rs>
                        fuerunt, que sunt videtur in loco supra <placeName ref="#places/3444"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >Mataluni</placeName>, propinquo Sancta Maria ad ipsa cappella ubi
                        Grauzufuli vocatur et in loco ubi Sausilianu vocatur, hoc est a <rs
                            key="#Fines">fine</rs> quomodo vadit ipsa <rs key="#Roads">bias
                            Beneventana</rs> et quomodo revolvit et vadit usque ad terra <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3448" key="#Churches">Sancti Nazarii</orgName>
                        et perexiit usque ad terra <name ref="Pandenolfus">Pandenolfi</name> qui
                        dicitur Asenareca et revolvit et vadit usque ad terra qui se nominat de <rs
                            key="#Slave #Royal_slave">serbi domnici</rs>, que vobis concessimus, et
                        da aliu capu <rs key="#Mountains">monte</rs>; infra has fines concessimus
                        vobis omnes <rs key="#Landed_possessions">territorias</rs> quantas in supra
                        dictis locis habuerunt et pertinuerunt <name ref="Adelpertus"
                            >Adelperto</name> filius <name ref="Alpertus">Aliperti</name> et <name
                            ref="Renovatus">Renobato</name> frater Renobati de Sasillanu et <name
                            ref="Martinus">Martino</name> et <name ref="Martinianus"
                            >Martiniano</name> et <name ref="Wualpuzulus">Gualpuzolo</name>, insimul
                        cum reliquas omnes <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Property_of_persons_without_heirs">terrias
                            exfundatas</rs> quantas infra supra dicte finis et in iam dictis locis
                        inventas dederit, sicut supra dictus Piniolus genitor vester a domno
                            <persName ref="#people/315" key="#Princeps">Landolfo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">glorioso</rs>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs> genitore nostro ei datum fuit et qualiter
                        ille ipsos possedit, sic vobis qui super germanis vestrisque heredibus ea
                        omnia concedimus abendi ac possidendi sine contrarietate comitis, gastaldei,
                        iudicis aut cuiuscumque persone contradictione vel inquietudine, sed
                        perpetuis temporibus vos et vestris heredibus habeatis et possideatis ea
                        omnia qualiter superius legitur et faciatis exinde omnia que volueritis,
                        nemine vobis exinde in aliquo contraria ingerente. Scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/337" key="#Notary">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ex iussio supra dicte potestatis in anno
                        duodecimo principatus eius, mense septembrio, decima indictione. Actum in
                            <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuana</placeName>.
                        Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
